schemas.assessmentDescription: Biodiversity assessment schema for Green Goods garden spaces. Captures soil health, carbon metrics, species diversity, and ecological observations to verify regenerative agriculture practices.
schemas.assessmentSchema: uint8 soilMoisturePercentage,uint256 carbonTonStock,uint256 carbonTonPotential,uint256 gardenSquareMeters,string biome,string remoteReportPDF,string speciesRegistryJSON,string[] polygonCoordinates,string[] treeGenusesObserved,string[] weedGenusesObserved,string[] issues,string[] tags
schemas.workApprovalDescription: Work approval schema for Green Goods protocol. Allows validators to approve or reject submitted work with feedback, enabling trustless verification of regenerative agriculture activities.
schemas.workDescription: Work submission schema for Green Goods protocol. Enables gardeners to submit completed regenerative agriculture tasks with media evidence and metadata for verification and payment.
schemas.workSchema: uint256 actionUID,string title,string feedback,string metadata,string[] media
